messages.text: It was a pleasure to chat Jack! Feel free to text me here if you have any questions or concerns. Here’s the link to the application if you haven’t received it: https://app.prodicity.org/
Will do

Perfect

https://calendly.com/theivanyeung/call

Let me know what times work for you and your parents next weekend 24/25th, morning/noon.

This message has been deleted.
That works, see you then!
Also any updates or breakthroughs on the baits?

Nothing huge yet, but I made more prototypes with the new solution and am pretty pleased with them. They feel like traditional baits with their flexibility/durability and are holding up well in storage.
Also, I think LinkedIn had a small glitch, but it showed your deleted message for a split second and actually 1 o clock would work better if it works for you.

1 would be better, I'll send you the zoom link 15 minutes prior to the call
I am excited, I should be able to put some hours in next weekend with them.
